      "summary": "You love seeing light bulbs go off in people’s eyes and walking with them as they grow. You take the time to explain concepts patiently and adapt your approach to the person in front of you. You track their progress and celebrate milestones along the way. You pay attention to the emotional undercurrents and adjust your pace and method to meet people where they are; your joy comes from watching others thrive and seeing knowledge take root. Whether over coffee or in a small group, you guide gently, balancing truth with care. This blend of clarity and compassion makes you a nurturer: you shepherd others through learning and make sure they feel supported on the journey.",
